clear
cat <<"EOT"
				TUX IS A BLACKARCHER
                 .88888888:. 
                88888888.88888. 
              .8888888888888888. 
              888888888888888888 
              88' _`88'_  `88888 
              88 88 88 88  88888 
              88_88_::_88_:88888 ~ Sup?
              88:::,::,:::::8888 
