             .88  `::::'    8:88. 
            8888            `8:888. 
          .8888'             `888888. 
         .8888:..  .::.  ...:'8888888:. 
        .8888.'     :'     `'::`88:88888 
       .8888        '         `.888:8888. 
      888:8     i3  . Archlinux 888:88888 
    .888:88        .:           888:88888: 
    8888888.       ::           88:888888 
    `.::.888.      ::          .88888888 
   .::::::.888.    ::         :::`8888'.:. 
  ::::::::::.888   '         .:::::::::::: 
  ::::::::::::.8    '      .:8::::::::::::. 
 .::::::::::::::.        .:888::::::::::::: 
 :::::::::::::::88:.__..:88888:::::::::::' 
  `'.:::::::::::88888888888.88:::::::::' 
        `':::_:' -- '' -'-' `':_::::'` 
